textAnnotations.description:
CLUB
NATO SAILING CLUB!
Looking for Opportunities to Sail?
There's a New NATO Sailing Club with
Sailing Events Including
Day Sails
Weekend Cruises
Longer European Cruises
Racing
Channel Crossings
Sailing Courses
LOOKING FOR SKIPPERS! ORGANISERS! PARTICIPANTS!
COMMITTEE MEMBERS!
OPEN TO ALL-EXPERIENCED AND THOSE WHO WANT
TO LEARN!
See us on Facebook Go to NATO Sailing Club
and request access
For more info please contact at NATO HQ:
President - Carol Gruppe +32 2 707 5787
Carol.gruppe@hq.nato.int
Or at SHAPE
Vice-President -Jan-Jakob Muyls
Jan-Jakob.MUYLS@shape.nato.int
